  "texts": [
    "To explore the effect of different data on the pre-trained model, in the supervised finetuning, we investigated different ratios of data, and empirically determined a 2:1 ratio between music scores and music knowledge&music summary data.",
    "We found that this ratio performed excellently in music generation as well as music understanding while guaranteeing a good MMLU performance.",
    "According to the 2:1 ratio, we first sampled 78K samples from the training set and trained for 10 epochs.",
    "Then, we maintained the ratio and utilized all available music scores data, which includes 1.1M samples, and trained for 2 epochs.",
    "The data mixture settings are summarized in Appendix E."
  ],
